Subject: [PATCH] Revise 'Tentang Kami' content to emphasize AC sales and
 product consultation

### Motivation
- Shift the About/Tentang pages from a service/repair focus to present Radja AC as a multibrand AC dealer and product-consultation partner.
- Make messaging consistent across hero, profile, and trust components to highlight product recommendations, procurement, installation, and after-sales support.
- Apply small formatting fixes such as normalizing import lines and ensuring EOF newlines.

### Description
- Update copy in `AboutHero.jsx` to promote Radja AC as a partner for multibrand AC sales and product selection.
- Replace profile content in `AboutProfile.jsx` to emphasize dealership, product choice, procurement, coordinated installation, and after-sales support, and update the feature list accordingly.
- Adjust `AboutTrust.jsx` items and CTA text to focus on product recommendations, brand variety, transparent purchasing, and after-sales support, including changing the WhatsApp heading to `Konsultasi produk via WhatsApp`.
- Update page metadata in `TentangKami.jsx` `SeoHead` `description` to reflect the sales/consultation positioning and perform minor import/format newline cleanups across modified files.

### Testing
- No automated tests were added or modified for this change.
- No automated test suite was executed as part of this content-only update.
